<pre><span style="color: rgba(0, 128, 128, 1)"> 1</span> [root@cs software]# <span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 255, 1)">ls</span> /data/mysql/<span style="color: rgba(128, 0, 128, 1)">3307</span>/
