<h3>4.7 启动</h3>
<p>到这里，多实例的配置基本完毕，可以尝试启动了</p>
<div class="cnblogs_code">
<pre><span style="color: rgba(0, 128, 128, 1)">1</span> <span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1)">systemctl start mysqld3307.service
</span><span style="color: rgba(0, 128, 128, 1)">2</span> <span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1)">systemctl start mysqld3308.service
</span><span style="color: rgba(0, 128, 128, 1)">3</span> systemctl start mysqld3309.service</pre>
</div>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>验证下：</p>
